rows.label: bf01100150_0010
rows.name:
Drivers...?
And...Blades?!

rows.label: bf01100150_0020
rows.name:
Whoa!
They look so cool!

rows.label: bf01100150_0030
rows.name: So... There's something that we want to haul up.

rows.label: bf01100150_0040
rows.name:
There were some current shifts. It showed up in an
uncharted area.

rows.label: bf01100150_0050
rows.name: But it's a long way down.

rows.label: bf01100150_0060
rows.name: Nice... I like a good challenge!

rows.label: bf01100150_0070
rows.name: [ML:undisp ] ...

rows.label: bf01100150_0080
rows.name:
Bahn offered to assemble
team of veterans for this job.

rows.label: bf01100150_0090
rows.name:
But this crew very picky. They want small
elite team, and only from Liberalitas.

rows.label: bf01100150_0100
rows.name: That when Bahn have stroke of genius!

rows.label: bf01100150_0102
rows.name: Should hire Rex!

rows.label: bf01100150_0110
rows.name: Hah-ha! You made the right choice!

rows.label: bf01100150_0120
rows.name: [ML:undisp ] *snicker*

rows.label: bf01100150_0130
rows.name: A child salvager?

rows.label: bf01100150_0140
rows.name:
Hey Shin, is this job doubling 
as a field trip for the kids?

rows.label: bf01100150_0150
rows.name:
Hey! You're one to talk - you look 
just as young as I do!

rows.label: bf01100150_0160
rows.name:
I wouldn't get all excited over pocket change 
unlike some certain fool.

rows.label: bf01100150_0170
rows.name: Who are you calling a fool?!

rows.label: bf01100150_0180
rows.name: Ah, you must be Rex-sama.

rows.label: bf01100150_0190
rows.name:
I implore you to excuse
my lady's discourtesy.

rows.label: bf01100150_0200
rows.name:
Byakko! 
Mind your own business for once!

rows.label: bf01100150_0210
rows.name: Cut it out, Nia!

rows.label: bf01100150_0212
rows.name: Though, I do see your point...

rows.label: bf01100150_0220
rows.name: In any case...

rows.label: bf01100150_0222
rows.name:
It should be easy enough
to make sure...

rows.label: bf01100150_0230
rows.name: What-?!

rows.label: bf01100150_0240
rows.name: Ugh!

rows.label: bf01100150_0250
rows.name: What're you playing at?!

rows.label: bf01100150_0260
rows.name: Well, well, well...

rows.label: bf01100150_0270
rows.name:
Metsu!
What good is it, beating up a kid?

rows.label: bf01100150_0280
rows.name:
You said it yourself, didn't you?
What if the kid's not up to it?

rows.label: bf01100150_0290
rows.name: I said nothing of the sort!

rows.label: bf01100150_0300
rows.name: You did think it though, right?

rows.label: bf01100150_0310
rows.name: And anyway, now we know.

rows.label: bf01100150_0320
rows.name:
You'll do right enough.
Though you don't look like a Driver...

rows.label: bf01100150_0330
rows.name: Where'd you learn those Arts?

rows.label: bf01100150_0340
rows.name: Gramps showed me a thing or two.

rows.label: bf01100150_0350
rows.name:
Even when I was little, that was his
idea of playtime.

rows.label: bf01100150_0360
rows.name:
Well, you've got some skill, I'll give
you that. Guts, too.

rows.label: bf01100150_0370
rows.name: Never mind, just get the job done.

rows.label: bf01100150_0380
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh!
Friends are such rowdy bunch!

rows.label: bf01100150_0390
rows.name: Here is advance.

rows.label: bf01100150_0400
rows.name:
Use to buy what gear you need,
then go to dock on starboard!

rows.label: bf01100150_0410
rows.name: Bahn has arranged excellent vessel for you there.

rows.label: bf01100150_0420
rows.name: You got it!
